Create a new post:

1. Create a new *.md file in the _posts folder, matching to format the other files use
2. Run "bundle exec jekyll serve --incremental" to build and deploy the site locally. It'll show the url to view the site at
3. Verify the new pages show up in the _site folder
4. Run "bundle exec jekyll clean" to remove stale generated files and let forestry generate them cleanly
4. Commit and push the changes
5. Verify the site deployed successfully (can take up to 5 minutes)
